Q1. What is the purpose of this wishlist vase?

This vase is designed to help you focus on your intentions and goals while enhancing your space with positive and growth-oriented energy.

Q2. What does Green Aventurine represent?

Green Aventurine is associated with luck, opportunities, and growth, making it ideal for manifestation and new beginnings.

Q3. What is the role of the Pyrite geode on top?

Pyrite is linked with wealth and abundance energy, adding a prosperity-focused element to the product.

Q4. How do I use this product?

You can place it on your desk, bedside, or workspace and use it as a visual reminder of your goals or intentions.

Q5. Is this a natural crystal product?

Yes, both Green Aventurine and Pyrite are natural crystals. Slight variations in shape, size, and texture are natural.

Q6. Does it require any maintenance?

No special maintenance is required. Simply keep it clean and place it in a space where you see it regularly.

Q7. Where should I place it for best results?

It works best on work desks, study areas, or personal spaces where focus, growth, and intention matter most.










